## 🧭 Helm Chart Architecture Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart TB

    subgraph Helm_Chart["Helm Chart (chart/ directory)"]
        A[Chart.yaml<br/>Chart metadata]
        B[values.yaml<br/>Default configuration values]
        C[templates/*.yaml<br/>K8s manifest templates]
        D[helpers.tpl<br/>Reusable template functions]
    end

    subgraph Helm_CLI["Helm CLI"]
        E[helm install / upgrade<br/>Render templates]
    end

    subgraph Rendered_Manifests["Rendered Kubernetes Manifests"]
        F[Deployment.yaml]
        G[Service.yaml]
        H[ConfigMap.yaml]
        I[Secret.yaml]
    end

    subgraph Kubernetes_Cluster["Kubernetes Cluster"]
        J[Deployment<br/>ReplicaSet → Pods]
        K[Service<br/>ClusterIP / NodePort / LoadBalancer]
        L[ConfigMap]
        M[Secret]
    end

    %% Flow
    A --> E
    B --> E
    C --> E
    D --> E

    E --> F
    E --> G
    E --> H
    E --> I

    F --> J
    G --> K
    H --> L
    I --> M
